shortDescription:
PRODUCT DETAILS
There should be no confusion about whether or not you need this top! This top has a trendy Paisley pattern with colors that are perfect for the season! It's comfortable for all day wear, has a figure-flattering fit, and features the split V neck design! Pair this top with skinnies and sneakers for an easy everyday outfit!

PRODUCT FEATURES
- Size: XL, 2XL, 3XL, 4XL
- Fabric: Material has generous amount of stretch and a silky, smooth feel
- Neck: Split V Neck Design
- Pattern: Floral
- Fit: Flare fit
- Sleeve: Roll-Up 3/4 Sleeve
- Waistline: Loose
- Hem: Curved hem
- Length: Tunic length
- Feature: Plus Size, Long Sleeve Tunic, V Neck, High Low Hem
- Style: Loose Tunic Blouse
- Stereotype: Flowy Tunic Shirts for Casual days or work.
- Suitable season: Spring, Summer, Autumn, Winter

FABRIC & CARE
- Material: 95% Polyester, 5% Spandex.
- Machine washable.

FIT & SIZING
- Standard US Plus Size in size dropdown list, please select the size you usually wear.
